            <p class="comment-content">流水账一样的故事叙述，捋了一遍各国演替，基础普及吧。看个热闹。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1194234923">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1194234923" class="vote-count">0</span>
